<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Child School Session Subscription Notification</title>
  </head>
  <body
    style="
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    "
  >
    <div
      style="
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        background-color: #fff;
        padding: 40px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      "
    >
      <h1 style="color: #333">
        Child School Session Subscription Notification
      </h1>
      <p style="color: #666">
        <%=first_name %>, Please note that your child bearing <%=child_name %>
        with email: <%=child_email %> needed to inform us at Christs' School
        whether he/she is joining us for the <%=academic_session %> academic
        session. Please login to your account or the account of this child to do
        the needful.
      </p>
      <p style="color: #666">
        If you are not expecting any mail from Topsun School, you can safely
        ignore this email.
      </p>
      <p style="color: #666; font-style: italic">
        Regards,<br />Topsun School Ado-Ekiti
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
